<H2>ADR: The Faegre Group</H2>
</CENTER>
<p>

The Faegre Group is an alternative dispute resolution consulting organization, operating as a division of Faegre & Benson.  It uses the principles of preventive law and conflict resolution to develop corporate programs to prevent disputes from occurring or, if they do occur, to manage and resolve disputes in an efficient and economic manner.<p>

