<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="intel3.gif"><P>

<H2>Intellectual Property Law</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>

Faegre & Benson counsels clients on strategies for protecting the valuable ideas, inventions and designs that constitute their intellectual property.<P>

Firm Lawyers admitted to the specialized practice of patent law prepare and prosecute patent applications both in the United States and abroad.  We handle trademark applications, oppositions, and cancellations in the United States Patent and Trademark Office.  We assist clients on domestic and international licensing and copyright matters, including the special issues associated with computer software and the unique problems posed by the work or artists and entertainers.<P>

We counsel clients on avoiding infringement of patents, trademark and copyrights, and advise clients on the creation and protection of trade secrets.<P>

Our intellectual property, copyright, trademark, trade secret, unfair competition and Lanham Act litigation involving a diverse range of subjects, including medical and biotechnology devices, computer software and hardware, graphic designs, popular song lyrics, motion pictures, electronic devices, consumer goods and industrial machinery.<P>

<H3>Areas of Practice</H3>

<UL>
Patents<BR>
Trademarks<BR>
Copyrights<BR>
Computer law<BR>
Trade secrets<BR>
Advertising law<BR>
Licensing<BR>
Unfair competition
</UL>


