<H2>International Business Law</H2>
</CENTER>
<p>

Through its United States, London, Frankfurt and Almaty offices, the Firm counsels domestic companies on the legal, financial, tax and regulatory matters affecting business operations in the international market.  The Firm also represents foreign businesses in connection with trading and investment in the United States.
