<H2>Real Estate Law</H2>
</CENTER>
<p>

Lawyers at the Firm are experienced in handling the sale and acquisition of commercial real estate.  They negotiate, develop and prepare financing and construction agreements and they assist landlords and tenants in the negotiation of commercial, industrial, office and retail leases.  Faegre & Benson advises clients on eminent domain, zoning, land use and title claim issues.<p>

