<H2>Denver, Colorado</H2>
</CENTER>

In Denver, Faegre & Benson provides legal services directed to the needs of the Colorado business and professional communities, as well as to companies based elsewhere that do business in the Rocky Mountain region.  The firm's senior lawyers in Denver have been engaged in the practice of law in Colorado for decades.  In several areas of practice, the work of the firm's Denver lawyers is nationally recognized.  This background enables Faegre & Benson to provide businesses and individuals throughout the region with experienced, skilled lawyers who are solidly grounded in the Colorado community.<p>

The lawyers in the Denver office work with lawyers in the firm's other offices to provide comprehensive services to their Rocky Mountain clients.  In addition, the Denver office makes available to Faegre & Benson's clients outside of Colorado legal services in practice areas in which the Denver lawyers have particular proficiency, including oil and gas, natural resources, health care, eminent domain, reorganization and bankruptcy.<P>

Faegre & Benson<BR>
2500 Republic Plaza<BR>
370 Seventeenth Street<BR>
Denver, Colorado  80202 4004<BR>
303-592-9000<P>

