<H2>Des Moines, Iowa</H2>
</CENTER>

Des Moines' growth as a regional center of business and commerce has brought an increased demand for legal services in Iowa.  In response to the growth, Faegre & Benson in 1990 became the first regional law firm to establish an Iowa office.  Through its Des Moines office, Faegre & Benson is able to provide clients headquartered in Iowa and clients having Iowa operations with comprehensive legal services through lawyers familiar with an Iowa-based practice.<p>

The firm's Des Moines partners are native Midwesterners with highly developed local practices.  They are active in Iowa community and professional matters and for many years have represented clients interests before the Iowa courts and before state and local agencies.<p>

Faegre & Benson long has served clients with business interests in Iowa from its office in Minneapolis.  Through the Des Moines office, we now can better serve those needs through established local lawyers who are able to work in concert with more than 275 Faegre & Benson lawyers in the firm's other offices.<p>

Faegre & Benson LLP<BR>
400 Capital Square<BR>
400 Locust Street<BR>
Des Moines, Iowa  50309-2331<BR>
Telephone:  515-248-9000<br>
Facsimile:  515-248-9010<p>

<A HREF="att_dsms.html">Attorneys</A><P>

