<td width=400>
<p align=left>

<FONT SIZE=+2>T</font>his seminar will provide an overview of strategies for protecting and maximizing the value of intellectual property in the course of mergers and acquisitions, financings, licensing, partnering and joint ventures as well as in relationships with employees, customers, suppliers and other business partners.  The focus will be on recurring issues such as representations and warranties, due diligence, confidentiality agreements, noncompete agreements and ownership and control of intellectual property.
