<HEAD><TITLE>1997 Intellectual Property - Changing Prescriptions for Intellectual Property in Medical Technology</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="backgrnd.gif" TEXT="#FFFFFF" LINK="#FF0000" VLINK="#FF7F76" ALINK="#EEDFFF"><BASEFONT SIZE=4>
<TABLE cellpadding=0>
<TR>
<TD width=120><FONT SIZE=+1 face="courier">Changing Prescriptions for Intellectual Property in Medical Technology
</FONT>
</TD>

<TD colspan=2 align=left><p align=center><IMG SRC="fb.gif" ALT="Letterhead GIF" HSPACE=25 ALIGN=absbottom><br>

<IMG SRC="clear.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=1>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td></td>

<td><IMG SRC="clear.gif" WIDTH=55 HEIGHT=10 hspace=20></TD>

<td width=400>
<p align=left>

<FONT SIZE=+2>I</font>ntellectual property laws of great importance to the medical technology industry are in a state of transition.  Congress recently enacted legislation which limits the remedies available against infringers of patented medical and surgical procedures.  District and Federal Circuit court decisions reflect a trend away from broad claim constructions and hostility toward the Doctrine of Equivalents as we await the Supreme Courts <EM>Hilton Davis</EM> decision.  Contracts for the acquisition and licensing of intellectual property rights continue to be critical to the successful commercialization of medical technology, and are therefore frequent topics of dispute.  In the future, the diagnosis and treatment of intellectual property issues in the medical technology field will clearly be enhanced by greater up-front focus on the patent application process and forward-thinking contract drafting.  This seminar session will describe these developments and address their impact on medical technology companies.
</p>
</td>
</tr>
<td>
</td>

<td colspan=2 align=center>

<A HREF="ip97.htm"><IMG SRC="invite.gif" WIDTH=66 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0></a>
<IMG SRC="splitter.gif" WIDTH=7 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0>
<A HREF="ip_sched.htm"> <IMG SRC="schedule.gif" WIDTH=67 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0></A>
<IMG SRC="splitter.gif" WIDTH=7 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0>
<A HREF="ip_regis.htm"> <IMG SRC="register.gif" WIDTH=77 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0></A>
<IMG SRC="splitter.gif" WIDTH=7 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0>
<A HREF="ip_topcs.htm"> <IMG SRC="topics.gif" WIDTH=49 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0></A>

<p align=center><i><font size=-1>
Copyright &copy; 1997 Faegre &amp; Benson LLP, all rights reserved.<font></i>

</p>
</td></tr></table>

