<HEAD><TITLE>1997 Intellectual Property - Intellectual Property in Transactions with the Government and Compliance with Government Export Controls</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="backgrnd.gif" TEXT="#FFFFFF" LINK="#FF0000" VLINK="#FF7F76" ALINK="#EEDFFF"><BASEFONT SIZE=4>
<TABLE cellpadding=0>
<TR>
<TD width=120><FONT SIZE=+1 face="courier">Intellectual Property in Transactions with the Government and Compliance with Government Export Controls
</FONT>
</TD>

<TD colspan=2 align=left><p align=center><IMG SRC="fb.gif" ALT="Letterhead GIF" HSPACE=25 ALIGN=absbottom><br>

<IMG SRC="clear.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=1>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td></td>

<td><IMG SRC="clear.gif" WIDTH=55 HEIGHT=10 hspace=20></TD>

<td width=400>
<p align=left>

<FONT SIZE=+2>T</font>ransactions with the Federal Government can take various forms, including supply contracts, service contracts, software development contracts, Cooperative Research and Development Agreements (CRADAs), and others.  In addition, companies engaged in the licensing or sale of intellectual property to foreign parties often fail to recognize that such transactions are subject to U.S. export control laws which can expose such companies to severe potential consequences if the laws are violated.  This presentation will discuss methods for protecting your intellectual property in government transactions and maximizing your rights in intellectual property resulting from such transactions.  The discussion will include recent developments under the Freedom of Information Act, Department of Defense software and technical data regulations, the impact of new commercial item acquisition procedures, and remedies for the governments violation of intellectual property rights.  An introduction to the scope and framework of U.S. export laws will be presented together with an update on recent developments in export controls on encryption software.
</p>
</td>
</tr>
<td>
</td>

<td colspan=2 align=center>

<A HREF="ip97.htm"><IMG SRC="invite.gif" WIDTH=66 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0></a>
<IMG SRC="splitter.gif" WIDTH=7 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0>

<A HREF="ip_sched.htm"> <IMG SRC="schedule.gif" WIDTH=67 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0></A>
<IMG SRC="splitter.gif" WIDTH=7 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0>

<A HREF="ip_regis.htm"> <IMG SRC="register.gif" WIDTH=77 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0></A>
<IMG SRC="splitter.gif" WIDTH=7 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0>

<A HREF="ip_topcs.htm"> <IMG SRC="topics.gif" WIDTH=49 HEIGHT=14 hspace=0></A>

<p align=center><i><font size=-1>
