<title>The Ogoni Community Association - UK Home Page</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#dc6000" link="#1c0b5a" alink="#ffff00" vlink="#5b0012">

<hr>
<h1 align=center>The Ogoni Community Association</h1>

<p align=center><font size=4><i>Lord take my soul, the struggle goes on</i></font>

<p><ul>
<li><a href="press_6feb.html">Shelling Nigeria Ablaze</a><br>
By Claude Ake<p>

<li><a href="ndm_jan9.html">Eyewitness Account - Ogoni Day 1996</a><br>
NDM News Release
<p>

<li><a href="events.html">Upcoming Events (update)</a>
<p>
