<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000560-B042-313</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/odi/3key.html 193.128.6.150 19970213102707 text/html 4928
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
