<ul>

<b><li><a href="jan97/brief.html">January 1997</a></b><br>
Features include the microfinance debate and the provision of small loans to poor people ignored by convemtional banks, and the Zambian copper miners whose lives are threatened by toxic fumes.<p>

<b><li><a href="dec96/brief.html">December 1996</a></b><br>
Features include articles on the EU's new relationship with the developing world, how Tutsis could trigger the end of colonial borders and women in Indian politics.<br>
<b><li><a href="nov96/brief.html">November 1996</a></b><br>
Features include pollution of China's Yellow river, why technocracy will not solve Pakistan's economic problems and how new found press freedom in Thailand will not stop the Thais rewriting history.<p>

