<li><b><a href="media17.html">Biodiversity: A matter of extinction</a></b><br> The profusion of plants, animals and micro-organisms is disappearing at an alarmingrate, threatening future food supplies and the making of new drugs. <p>




<li><b><a href="panos_internet_press.html">The Internet and the South: Superhighway or dirt-track?</a></b><br>
Highlights the pros and cons of the internet for the developing world.<p> 

<li><b><a href="panos_eco2.html">Ecotourism</a></b></ul><p> 




<hr><b>Panos London:</b><br>
9 White Lion Street. London. N1 9PD. UK<br>
Tel: +44-(0)171 278 1111<br>
Fax: +44-(0)171 278 0345<br>
Email: <a href="mailto:panoslondon@gn.apc.org">panoslondon@gn.apc.org</a><br
>URL http://www.oneworld.org/panos/<p>

