<html>
<header>
<title>EU Cooperation with Asia and Latin America</title>
</header>
<hr>
<H3><center><IMG SRC  = "images/eu.jpg">
<h3>EU Cooperation with Asia and Latin America<br>La coop&#233;ration de l'UE avec l'Asie et l'Am&#233;rique latine</h3>
</center>
<p>
<hr>
<h5>
<ul>
<li><A HREF="../aprodev/centam.htm">APRODEV Background Note on EU-Central America Relations</a>. (<i>APRODEV, October 1996</i>)
<P>
<LI><A HREF="../liaison/news/ln21f_17.htm">Apprendre les uns des autres : l'UE et l'Inde</A>. (<I>Liaison Info, octobre 1996</I>) 
<P>
<li><a href="dandc/95s_biz.htm">Aproximaciones: nuevas modalidades de cooperaci&oacute;n UE-Mercosur</a>. (<i>D+C Desarrollo y Cooperaci&#243;n, julio-agosto 1995</i>)
<P>
<li><a href="cidob/raizer.htm">La cooperaci&oacute;n cient&iacute;fica y tecnol&oacute;gica entre la Comunidad Europea y Am&eacute;rica Latina</a>. (<i>Revista CIDOB d'Afers Internacionals, 1995</i>) 
<p>
<LI><A HREF="../liaison/news/ln23e_14.htm">Europe-Asia relations: Follow-up of the official and NGO ASEM process</a>. (<i>Liaison News, December 1996-January 1997</i>)  <IMG SRC="images/new.gif">
<p>
<li><a href="http://europa.eu.int/en/comm/dg1b/en/den-com95495.htm" target="_top">The European Union and Latin America: The present situation and prospects for closer partnership, 1996-2000</a>. (<i>European Commission, October 1995</i>)
<p>
<li><a href="cidob/fernando.htm">La nueva pol&iacute;tica exterior de la Uni&oacute;n Europea y los pa&iacute;ses miembros del Pacto Andino</a>. (<i>Revista CIDOB d'Afers Internacionals, 1996</i>) 
<P>
<LI><A HREF="../liaison/news/ln23f_14.htm">Relations Asie-Europe: suivi du processus officiel (ASEM) et du processus ONG</a>. (<i>Liaison info, d&#233;cembre 1996-janvier 1997</i>)  <IMG SRC="images/new.gif">
<p>
<LI><A HREF="../liaison/news/ln21e_17.htm">Towards learning from each other: the EU and India</A>. (<I>Liaison News, October 1996</I>) 
<p>
<li><a href="cidob/ayuso.htm">La relaci&oacute;n euro-latinoamericana a trav&eacute;s del
proceso de integraci&oacute;n regional europea</a>. (<i>Revista CIDOB d'Afers Internacionals, 1995</i>) <IMG SRC="images/new.gif">
<p>
<li><a href="ajds/ajds8.htm">The revival of Latin American co-operation and the EC</a>. (<i>Austrian Journal of Development Studies, 1992</i>)
<p>
<li><a href="http://europa.eu.int/en/comm/dg1b/fr/dfr-com95495.htm" target="_top">Union europ&#233;ene-Am&#233;rique latine: Actualit&#233; et perspectives du renforcement du partenariat, 1996-2000</a>. (<i>Commission europ&#233;enne, octobre 1995</i>)
<p>
<li><a href="cidob/laporte.htm">La Uni&oacute;n Europea y el Cono Sur emprenden la reconciliaci&oacute;n</a>. (<i>Revista CIDOB d'Afers Internacionals, 1995</i>) <IMG SRC="images/new.gif">

<p>
</ul>
